title: Your Comfort Zone is Killing Your Dreams
itunes:title: Your Comfort Zone is Killing Your Dreams
description:
Your comfort zone is where your dreams go to die. In this episode, I am going to talk about how important it is to push the boundaries of what you feel is possible for yourself and why you should force yourself to never be comfortable. 

Follow me on IG for more ❤️ https://instagram.com/robdialjr
